        <a href="/2023/02/21/three-tips-for-using-facebook-and-instagram-stories/">Three Tips for Using Facebook and Instagram Stories</a>
      </h3>
      <p>At USA.gov and USAGov en Español, we’re always looking for better ways to connect people to government information through social media. Using stories has helped us increase our engagement rate and our number of followers as we deliver helpful information to people. Stories may be a good addition to your agency’s social media strategy, too. These three tips can help you get started.
          <em class="card__source source">— via <a href="https://blog.usa.gov/three-tips-for-using-facebook-and-instagram-stories" title="Read at USA.gov">USA.gov</a></em>
        
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card__media">
    <img src="/logos/usagov-logo.png" alt="USA.gov logo">
  </div>
  <div class="card__meta">
    <p class="date">Feb 21, 2023</p>
  </div>
</article>

            




